            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Docusaurus Plushie" src="/assets/images/docusaurus-plushie-banner-a60f7593abca1e3eef26a9afa244e4fb.jpeg" width="1500" height="500" class="img_ev3q"></p><p>I started my website with <a href="https://docusaurus.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus</a> and <a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Pages</a>. Building this website is pretty fun and I learned a lot of new things. I hope that I can keep updating content and make this website show on the Google search result.  </p><p>I wrote a note about how to build a website with Docusaurus and GitHub Pages. If anyone is interested, please take a look at <a href="/docs/docusaurus/start-with-github-pages">Start with GitHub Pages</a>, and my website source code is on <a href="https://github.com/eddielin0926/eddielin0926.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
